<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idd2299da3-4ef6-11f1-9110-db228fde61c5" identifier="/us/usc/t47/s31"><num value="31">§ 31.</num><heading> Summary trials</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The provisions of sections 391–396 of title 33 shall extend to the trial of offenses against the provisions of sections 24 and 25 of this title.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idd2299da4-4ef6-11f1-9110-db228fde61c5">(<ref href="/us/act/1888-02-29/ch17/s11">Feb. 29, 1888, ch. 17, § 11</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/25/42">25 Stat. 42</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
